SecuGen.FDxSDKPro.jni
Class SGFDxErrorCode

java.lang.Object
  SecuGen.FDxSDKPro.jni.SGFDxErrorCode

public abstract class SGFDxErrorCode
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains static values for SecuGen FDx SDK Pro Error messages. These values are returned by methods in the JSGFPLib class.

See Also:
JSGFPLib
